{
  "stem": "21817.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And over the years, over the weeks and months, we, we acquired more guns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And lately in end of 19 3, winter 19 3 and beginning of '94, the early part--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943, I'm sorry, '43 and beginning of 1944, the-- some of the Partisans can't contact already with regular army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to parachute with packages, actually boxes with ammunition and guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no communication, I mean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember once we were waiting for a, for a plane to drop us some, some guns and ammunition, and only-- it looks like somebody had some contact with the army.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They made a big fire in, in the woods, like an envelope, you made two, four, five, five fires when you are in the air and you're in the middle of the woods.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were some places that were, that were actually-- there were no-- nothing was growing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could see the fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once they dropped us some, some guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had ammunition, and we had also dynamite.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was very risky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Many times they threw it down, and we never got it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The contacts were, were very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, even the ex-soldiers or ex-officers, they did not have good contact.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But later, when they had some paratroopers, they threw it on also paratroopers in, in the area, that they had better contact with the, with the front lines.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If they wanted to catch somebody, once in a while, they will catch a high officer, a German officer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They brought them to the front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They went through the front line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They brought them over on the Soviet side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a daily basis, we had the password for a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we knew each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
